cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.PL, cs.CC 

This paper deals with a temporal-epistemic logic and its model checking problem, which are topics that are typically studied in the areas of logic (cs.LO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of regular expressions to extend the semantics of the logic may also be of interest to researchers in the areas of language and automata theory (cs.LG) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper's focus on complexity results and algorithmic techniques may also make it relevant to the area of computational complexity (cs.CC).
